#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:25
msgid "Hardware"
msgstr "硬件"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:27
msgid ""
"The verified configuration uses one Atlas A3 node with 16 NPUs and 64 GB "
"HBM per NPU. The real-weight run used about 58 GB process memory per NPU "
"after startup."
msgstr ""
"已验证的配置使用一个 Atlas A3 节点，包含16个NPU，每个NPU 64 GB HBM。实际权重运行启动后每个NPU约使用58 GB进程内存。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:29
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:31
msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run Hy3-preview directly. For "
"Atlas A3 machines, select the image variant with the `-a3` suffix. The "
"official image already includes the vLLM and vLLM Ascend runtime needed "
"for the verified serving path."
msgstr ""
"您可以直接使用官方 Docker 镜像运行 Hy3-preview。对于 Atlas A3 机器，请选择带有 `-a3` 后缀的镜像变体。官方镜像已包含验证服务路径所需的 vLLM 和 vLLM Ascend 运行时。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:70
msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr ""
"此外，如果您不想使用上述 Docker 镜像，也可以从源码构建所有组件："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:72
msgid ""
"Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md)."
msgstr ""
"从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/docs/source/installation.md)。"

