#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:78
msgid "Run `vllm serve` from `/workspace`."
msgstr "在 `/workspace` 目录下运行 `vllm serve`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:101
msgid ""
"`--enable-ep-weight-filter` is optional. It skips expert weights that do "
"not belong to the local EP rank during loading, reducing disk and host-"
"memory pressure for very large MoE checkpoints. We recommend keeping it "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"`--enable-ep-weight-filter` 为可选参数。它在加载时跳过不属于本地 EP rank 的专家权重，减少超大 MoE 检查点的磁盘和主机内存压力。建议保持启用。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:102
msgid ""
"Tool calling and reasoning are service interfaces declared in the Hy3 "
"README, so it is recommended to pass the corresponding `hy_v3` parsers by"
" default."
msgstr ""
"工具调用和推理是 Hy3 README 中声明的服务接口，因此建议默认传递相应的 `hy_v3` 解析器。"

