#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Hy3-preview.md:175
msgid ""
"The following numbers are from a real-weight smoke benchmark on one Atlas"
" A3 16-NPU node, using TP16 + EP + MTP + ACLGraph. The benchmark used "
"`vllm bench serve`, random prompts, output length 128, `--max-concurrency"
" 1`, `--temperature 0`, and 4 requests per input length. These numbers "
"are functional performance evidence, not tuned throughput limits."
msgstr ""
"以下数据来自单个 Atlas A3 16-NPU 节点上的实际权重冒烟基准测试，使用 TP16 + EP + MTP + ACLGraph。基准测试使用 `vllm bench serve`，随机提示，输出长度128，`--max-concurrency 1`，`--temperature 0`，每个输入长度4个请求。这些数据为功能性能验证，并非调优后的吞吐量上限。"

